    <sec>
      <title>Background</title>
      <p>The navigation posture described here supplements the plain-text overview in
        <ext-link ext-link-type="wiki" xlink:href="mission-wiki.wiki">Mission Knowledge Base</ext-link>
        and the AsciiDoc log contained in <ext-link ext-link-type="asciidoc" xlink:href="celestial-navigation-notes.adoc">Helios Navigation Operations Log</ext-link>.
        Quantitative tables referenced below are sourced from the TSV data set
        <ext-link ext-link-type="data" xlink:href="resource-allocation.tsv">resource-allocation.tsv</ext-link>.</p>
    </sec>
    <sec>
      <title>Delta-V Ledger</title>
      <p>The delta-v budget aligns with the math derivations maintained in <ext-link ext-link-type="tex" xlink:href="navigation-theory.tex">Navigation Theory</ext-link>
        and the summary captured in the Typst manuscript <ext-link ext-link-type="typst" xlink:href="navigation-overview.typst">Navigation Overview</ext-link>.</p>
